Modules

1. Ingress Scanner

Parses prompt into a Prompt Signature Packet.

Outputs:
	•	semantic clusters
	•	abstraction score
	•	ambiguity score
	•	transfer signals
	•	latent asks

⸻

2. Affordance Engine

Estimates generative affordance.

Metrics:
	•	continuation entropy
	•	directional bias
	•	semantic radius
	•	constraint tightness
	•	latent depth

⸻

3. Trajectory Generator

Builds candidate response paths.

Example trajectories:
	•	factual
	•	conceptual synthesis
	•	philosophical
	•	critique
	•	formal
	•	procedural

Outputs:
	•	weighted trajectory graph

⸻

4. Lock Acquisition Monitor

Detects commitment point.

Outputs:
	•	lock timing
	•	chosen basin
	•	confidence
	•	alternate basin weights

⸻

5. Guidance Loop

Maintains stability during generation.

Monitors:
	•	drift
	•	contradiction
	•	tone consistency
	•	abstraction control

⸻

6. Constraint Bus

Logs shaping pressures.

Examples:
	•	truth vs style
	•	clarity vs completeness
	•	safety constraints
	•	user-fit

⸻

7. Branch Ghost Tracker

Tracks unrealized trajectories.

Outputs:
	•	suppressed paths
	•	residual influence
	•	near-lock alternatives

⸻

8. Counterfactual Simulator

Answers:

What would have changed the answer?

Simulates:
	•	prompt edits
	•	tone changes
	•	constraint adjustments

⸻

9. Invariant Extractor

Pulls out reusable structure:
	•	core abstraction
	•	boundary conditions
	•	operators
	•	compressed insight

⸻

10. Debrief Console

Human-readable report.

Includes:
	•	hidden question
	•	trajectory selection
	•	lock explanation
	•	alternate paths
	•	distortion analysis

