Failure Modes

Failure	Description	Fix
False Lock	wrong trajectory chosen early	delay commitment
Drift	answer wanders	tighten guidance
Basin Bleed	mixed modes	enforce basis
Overcompression	loses nuance	preserve branches
Ambiguity Sprawl	no convergence	increase direction


